item.title: SoftLayer_Billing_Item_Network_Message_Delivery
item.description: SoftLayer_Billing_Item_Network_Message_Delivery Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Billing_Item_Network_Message_Delivery data describes the related billing item. seeAlso SoftLayer_Billing_Item SoftLayer_Network_Message_Delivery Local allowCancellationFlag Flag to check if a billing item can be cancelled. 1 = yes. 0 = no. Type: integer associatedBillingItemId This is sometimes populated for orphan billing items that are not attached to servers. Billing items like secondary portable IP addresses fit into this category.
